{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">知道镁可以与盐酸反应产生氢气。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Mg + 2HCl&nbsp;= MgCl<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;+ H<sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">&uarr;</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管、药匙。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：镁粉、稀盐酸。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在试管中加入少量镁粉，然后加入少量稀盐酸，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">试管中有气泡产生。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}